Package tests

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DemoTest
    This is the class used for the final demo run.
    FinalTesting
    The class used for the integration testing.
    LightSensorTests
    Test class to determine the light value threshold and to check the functionality of the light sensor.
    NavigationTest
    Test class for different components of the navigation class, including travelTo, turnTo, fireAt And obstacle avoidance.
    OdoCalibration
    Test class to determine the constants defined in the odometer, like radius of the wheels and the distance of the wheels.
    OdoTesting
    Test class for odometer functionality and the accuracy of the reported values.
    OdoTestingTouch
    Testing of the odometer by using touch sensor for ease of the use.
    ReloaderTest
    Test class for the functionality of the reloader of the launcher component.
    ReloaderTouch
    Test class for the reloader component.
